:0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c284c113295410da3f3ada62f018b4705a2dec73","tid":2419000,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd58608b388143715d542581d26a055a34a46d91","tid":2419000,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:44:16.000Z","msg":"包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ebc24a6a70b01c7ff14998c9b33a1bce50705e","tid":2419000,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"網民 2019 年 11 月 11 日發起多區堵路行動，20 歲港大男學生被指於大埔公路投擲防撞杆，早前被裁定公眾地方造成阻礙罪成，遭裁判官陳炳宙判囚 2 個月，獲准保釋等候上訴。上訴聆訊今於高等法院進行，法官彭寶琴今聽罷雙方陳詞後，駁回港大生就定罪及判刑的上訴，並撤銷其保釋，須即時服刑，稍後頒布詳細書面判詞。<br />\n<br />\n部分到庭旁聽親友聞後表現失落，並向上訴人大叫「撐住呀，等你出嚟」，有親友眼泛淚光，上訴人則表現平靜。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官陳炳宙早前判刑時，狠批被告草菅人命，完全罔顧市民利益，又指他無權以堵路方式阻止他人上班、上學，質疑他如果真的關心社會，根本不會做出傷害社會的事。裁判官更明言「如果對被告過份寬大，就是對守法市民殘忍」。他又指，本案屬同類罪行中最嚴重，並非一般小販擺放雜物於行人路。被告與另一名女子向主要交通交匯處拋擲 3 枝防撞杆時，涉案警員的私家車正迎他們方向前進，被告與其共犯不可能不知，但仍拋擲防撞杆。當防撞杆在半空時，杆與私家車相距 10 米半，並在私家車前 4 米著地。若私家車駛得更快，結果不堪設想；若司機欠缺駕駛經驗，早就被嚇至驚惶失措，可能造成交通意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-2-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E%E9%A0%88%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-2-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv33aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=2698f6c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-2-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=a9dd6a9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-2-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E%E9%A0%88%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91/</a>"}]}